{"html":"<!-- TITLE: Emoji --><!-- SUBTITLE: A quick summary of Emoji --><html><head></head><body><p>EmojiOne plugin gives users a set of libraries to convert native emojis from devices to EmojiOne emoji.</p>\n<h1 id=\"basic-usage\"><a class=\"toc-anchor nc-icon-outline location_bookmark-add internal-link\" href=\"#basic-usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a> Basic Usage</h1>\n<p>Reference Site: <a href=\"https://github.com/emojione/emojione\" class=\"external-link\">https://github.com/emojione/emojione</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a class=\"toc-anchor nc-icon-outline location_bookmark-add internal-link\" href=\"#installation\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a> Installation</h2><div class=\"indent-h2\"><p><code>$npm install emojione</code></p></div>\n\n<h2 id=\"declaration\"><a class=\"toc-anchor nc-icon-outline location_bookmark-add internal-link\" href=\"#declaration\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a> Declaration</h2><div class=\"indent-h2\"><p><code>import * as emoji from &apos;emojione&apos;;</code></p></div>\n\n<h2 id=\"types-of-usage\"><a class=\"toc-anchor nc-icon-outline location_bookmark-add internal-link\" href=\"#types-of-usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a> Types of Usage</h2><div class=\"indent-h2\"><p><code>.toShort(str)</code> - converts native unicode emoji input(from mobile device) to their corresponding shortnames.</p><p><code>.shortnameToImage(str)</code> - converts shortnames directly to EmojiOne images.</p><p><code>.toImage(str)</code> - converts input containing both native unicode emoji and shortnames into EmojiOne images.</p></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"demo\"><a class=\"toc-anchor nc-icon-outline location_bookmark-add internal-link\" href=\"#demo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a> Demo</h2><div class=\"indent-h2\"><p><img src=\"/uploads/mygif.gif\" alt=\"Mygif\" title=\"Mygif\"></p></div>\n\n</body></html>","meta":{"title":"Emoji","subtitle":"A quick summary of Emoji","path":"plugins/emoji"},"tree":[{"content":"Basic Usage","anchor":"basic-usage","nodes":[{"content":"Installation","anchor":"installation","nodes":[]},{"content":"Declaration","anchor":"declaration","nodes":[]},{"content":"Types of Usage","anchor":"types-of-usage","nodes":[]},{"content":"Demo","anchor":"demo","nodes":[]}]}],"parent":{"path":"plugins","title":"Plugins","subtitle":"A quick summary of Plugins"}}